      "asbval:note": "DeepSAT outputs predictions for Morgan fingerprints, molecular weights, and structure classes (confirmed in passages 4, 5). Supplementary figures S1-S2 reference input/output windows from DeepSAT web interface, but the passages do not explicitly describe JSON response format or API response structure. Output format is inferred from the web platform description, not explicitly documented as JSON API responses.",
