      "asbval:evidence_quote": "the convolutional neural network extracts the features from HSQC spectra. Based on the extracted features, fully connected layers predict Morgan fingerprints, molecular weights, and chemical classes... The structure similarities were calculated using the chemical fingerprint method with cosine scoring.",
